snippet.title: Elden Ring Patch 1.04 The Greatsword Vs The Grafted Blade Greatsword (Dual Wield)
snippet.description:
The new Elden Ring 1.04 patch just gave an update to Colossal Weapons, which is a faster attack speed. There was also a damage increase buff to the Grafted Greatsword.

The Build:

Flask Of Wonderous Physick:
Strength-knot Crystal Tear
Spiked Cracked Tear

Flame, Grant Me Strength
Max Lvl Golden Order Seal

Royal Knight's Resolve Skill
(Greatswords)

Oath Of Vengeance Skill
(The Grafted Blade Greatswords)

Maxed Level Greatswords and Grafted Greatswords
